I'll neOne Black Russian., also.

29:04.284 --> 29:06.202
Yeah, it's for a business
contact I'm meeting here

29:06.286 --> 29:08.329
to discuss future growth
potential <i> for The Beat.</i>

29:09.414 --> 29:11.374
Hey.

29:11.458 --> 29:13.710
JHi.t!

29:13.793 --> 29:15.753
{\an1}Weren't you supposed to be
at the movies with your mom?

29:15.837 --> 29:17.213
Yeah, she's not feeling well.

29:17.297 --> 29:18.882
So, what'd you do,
leave her home alone?

29:18.965 --> 29:20.175
Steve, she has a headache.

29:20.258 --> 29:21.926
I just came by,
hoping to find you.

29:23.511 --> 29:25.221
One Black Russian
for the lady.

29:25.305 --> 29:26.264
Um, I don't drink
Black Russians.

29:26.347 --> 29:27.974
I thought maybe you'd like to

29:28.057 --> 29:29.726
tUh, why would you

29:29.809 --> 29:32.020
order me a drink if you
thought I was at the movies?

29:33.938 --> 29:35.440
Well...

29:35.523 --> 29:38.359
Steve Sanders?

29:38.443 --> 29:39.694
Lilly Samples.

29:39.777 --> 29:42.363
{\an1}Hi. Lilly.

29:42.447 --> 29:43.907
This is Janet;
we work together.

29:44.782 --> 29:46.201
Hi there.

29:46.284 --> 29:48.203
Um, can I get
a Black Russian, please?

29:48.286 --> 29:50.163
Sure.

29:52.499 --> 29:54.125
So, Lilly, how do you
like the Love Fisher?

29:54.792 --> 29:57.212
So far so good.

